MEP Business Manager
- ,
Date Posted: 2014/05/04 11:47:35
Ref. JB3047097
Job Description
MEP Business Manager, Dubai based for an international engineering consultant Package 60-70,000 / month A global brand, our Clients are a multi-disciplined engineering consultant; with a global staff matrix and office network. They have been based in Dubai for over ten years, providing design engineering consultancy services to the United Arab Emirates, Qatar and Saudi Arabia clients. Reporting to a Global MEP Leader (MEP) with operational reporting at Regional & Country Director level, the MEP Business Manager shall define and execute the Dubai based MEP strategy for the company. Supported by an established facades and civil structural engineering teams; the teams are providing design services for 5 star holiday resorts, mixed use developments and 4 star hotels in Dubai. Working with end-users, architects and with the Expo2020, our Clients are pursuing the strategy in increase their opportunities to work with major construction companies on a design & build basis.
Skills
To be considered you will need to have: Tertiary education from a recognizable university with professional qualifications; 15-20 years MEP design consultancy experience; Current Dubai MEP market knowledge were you have successfully defined and lead winning work strategies for mega 5 star projects Our Clients are seeking a talented, dedicated MEP Business Manager to shape their future MEP strategy for the Middle East. There is no ‘glass ceiling’, our Clients expect to employ 20,000 by year 2020 and these are exciting times to join their versatile, multi-disciplined engineering consultancy. Further information; please contact Ikram Rabbani on +971-55-585-2977.
